{"about_the_game":"Step into the role of the ruler of your own medieval settlement, manage and develop it in real-time from a first-person perspective.<br><br>Switch between 4 modes (<i>Free</i>, <i>Building</i>, <i>Ruler</i>, and <i>Combat</i>) to have simple control over everything around you.<br><br>Protect the Town Hall, which is the center of your settlement, and prevent the enemy from destroying it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/Title_1_-_EN.png?t=1737401503\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/DL_GIF_1.gif?t=1737401503\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Extract 5 types of resources.<br></li><li> Receive golden chests for developing your settlement.<br></li><li> Produce arrows in the archery workshop.<br></li><li> Look for berry bushes to provide food for your subjects.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/Title_2_-_EN.png?t=1737401503\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/DL_GIF_2.gif?t=1737401503\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Upgrade the Town Hall.<br></li><li> Build 8 types of buildings.<br></li><li> Manage your settlement from the management panel.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/Title_3_-_EN.png?t=1737401503\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348440/extras/DL_GIF_3.gif?t=1737401503\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Search for resources on the map.<br></li><li> Search and collect or eat mushrooms.<br></li><li> Destroy enemy camps.<br></li><li> Liberate the Watchtowers.<br></li><li> Take control of the Mines.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://sha